  "prompt": "I got 753 rank in Aiims and I have not attended to 1 at counseling. will I am eligible for second and third counseling?",
  "response": "Yes, you are still eligible for the second and third rounds of counseling for AIIMS even if you did not attend the first round. \n\nHere\u2019s how it works:\n\n- **Second Counseling:** If seats remain vacant after the first round of counseling, candidates like you who did not attend the first round (or were not allocated a seat) can participate in the second round. Your rank (753) will still be considered for seat allocation based on availability during the second round.\n\n- **Third Counseling:** If seats remain unfilled after the second round, a third round of counseling may be conducted. You will again be eligible to participate if you haven\u2019t secured a seat by then.\n\nIt\u2019s important to keep an eye on the official AIIMS counseling schedule and notifications to ensure you don\u2019t miss the registration or choice-filling deadlines for the subsequent rounds. Good luck!",
